                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">There are 3 types of enchaters now as I see it.
<br />

<br />
1) Those that think the class is fine and continue to play.
<br />

<br />
2) Those that think the class is lacking yet continue to play.
<br />

<br />
3) Those that think the class is lacking and have retired.
<br />

<br />
When I rant I guess I'm talking to types 1 and 2 to either make the 1's into 2's and maybe even make the 2's into 3's.  heheh  I'm almost certain that the ONLY way to ever get SoE to lift a finger to REALLY help our class (note: no bones, a REAL fix) is for ALL of us to become type 3's.  As long as there is an appreciable amount of 1's and 2's SoE will not do anything.  
<br />

<br />
Ergo, if I ever come off as rude to you it's because deep down I feel you're doing our class harm by continuing to play them.  Ludicrous isn't it?  I know and I'm trying to deal with it.  Even though I know there's a glimmer of truth to that I know there's very little I can do about it and I should just be happy that you're happy, or something like that.
<br />

<br />
If I get bad simply ignore me and move along. <img src="images/smiles/icon_razz.gif" alt="icon_razz.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />WoW > EQ
<br />
WoW > EQ2
<br />
Blizzard > SOE
<br />
/flip</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
